Package: vtamR
Type: Package
Title: Validation and Taxonomic Assigment of Metabarcoding data with R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Emese", 
           family = "Meglecz", 
           email = "emese.meglecz@imbe.fr", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: VTAM (Gonzalez et al, 2023) rewritten and extended in R. 
    A set of functions to handle and analyze metabarcoding datasets,
    including wrappers for external tools such as VSEARCH, BLAST, Cutadapt,
    and Swarm, with support for pipeline execution and result parsing.
